title: 820-3476 Airport test and load test errors
message:
Hi,
It is a clean board, which gives no errors when running Macbook internal diagnostic (D key). WIFI and Bluetooth work fine.
On the other hand when I run the ASD 3S162, I got errors on load test and airport test, see attached (ignore the first sensor group error, I simply did not have the DC in)

I replaced the WIFI card, I/O board, I/O connector, with the same results.

Any idea about what can generate these errors?

title: 820-3476 Airport test and load test errors
message:
If machine performs good unde macOS, don't bother with ASD report.
You can run HWMonitor, in case you note some strange behavior.

ALS, webcamera and keyboard backlight work correctly?

title: 820-3476 Airport test and load test errors
message:
ALS, camera, keyboard and LCD backlights are good.
HWMonitor has no strange values except for Airport at 129ºC, but I have this value also in good Macbooks. In any case the fan is running normal, increasing only when loaded

I will use this Macbook for a few days and see if anything bad happens
